'''Moussa Touré''' (wavutse 1958), ni umukinnyi wa [[Senegali|firime]] muri Sénégalese.   Azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa firime ''zizwi cyane Toubab Bi'', ''TGV'' na ''La Pirogue''<ref>https://africanfilmny.org/directors/moussa-toure/</ref> <ref>https://www.allocine.fr/film/fichefilm_gen_cfilm=206433.html</ref>.  Usibye icyerekezo, ni umutekinisiye, umwanditsi, producer n'umukinnyi.<ref>https://www.nytimes.com/2013/01/23/movies/the-pirogue-directed-by-moussa-toure.html</ref>  

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Touré yavutse 1958 i Dakar, muri [[Senegali]]<ref>https://iffr.com/en/persons/moussa-tour%C3%A9</ref>. 

== Umwuga ==
Yatangiye umwuga wa sinema nkumutekinisiye. Hanyuma mu 1987, yerekeje kuri firime akoresheje firime ngufi maze ashinga uruganda rwe bwite rwitwa 'Les Films du Crocodile'<ref>http://africultures.com/personnes?no=4305</ref>. Mu 1991, Touré yakoze filime ye ya mbere yerekana ''Toubab Bi'' .  yahawe ibihembo muri  Cannes Film Festival <ref>https://africanfilmny.org/directors/moussa-toure/</ref><ref>https://www.jeuneafrique.com/141448/societe/moussa-tour-aller-cannes-c-est-un-bonheur-et-une-lourde-responsabilit/</ref>. Nyuma yo gutsinda kwa mbere, yakoze film ye ya kabiri ''TGV'' mu 1998 abifashijwemo na Makéna Diop. Nyuma mu 1999, filime yegukanye igihembo cyabaterankunga mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya 9 rya [[Afurika]]<ref>https://en.unifrance.org/movie/15455/tgv</ref>. 

Mu 1996, yagize uruhare runini muri filime ''Les Caprices d'un rivière'' iyobowe na Bernard Giraudeau<ref>https://www.trigon-film.org/fr/directors/Moussa_Tour%C3%A9</ref> . Muri 2005, yakoze documentaire ''5x5'' yakiriwe neza.  Muri 2011, Touré yagizwe Umuyobozi w'Inteko y'abacamanza mu 2011 Iserukiramuco rya Filime na Televiziyo bya Panafrican rya Ouagadougou (FESPACO). Hanyuma muri 2012, yayoboye filime ye ya gatatu yerekana ''La Pirogue'', filime yerekana igice. Filime yafashwe amashusho kandi ihindurwa hifashishijwe imikorere ya Hollywood<ref>https://www.imdb.com/name/nm0869715/</ref>. Muri 2020, yayoboye filime ''Red Dust'' ikorwa na Luxembourgish yambaye imyenda ya BAHN na Dakar ikorera mu nzu itunganyirizwamo 'Les Films du Crocodile'. Filime izasohoka mu 2022<ref>https://cineuropa.org/en/newsdetail/375680/</ref>. 

